"You think that you know how beautiful someone is before you marry them. 💍 You've gone to weddings, galas and fancy dinners together — you've done it all. But when the doors opened and I saw @DrFatiMD in that @PninaTornai dress, arm-in-arm with her father as tears streamed down his cheeks, I was stunned,” says @RukusLive. 😍

“I never imagined I could see Fati look more beautiful than I already knew she was. 👰‍♀️ It's like she shimmered and floated down the aisle – there was an audible gasp from the crowd, so I knew it wasn't just me. 😱She was so angelic. She smiled hard at me in that moment, as if to remind me that it was just us. ✨It felt like the room disappeared and was the two of us on a cloud, becoming one. ☁️ 

Fati and I didn't meet in some fairytale setting — it was a packed nightclub and I felt she was too good to be true. 💭 After our first few dates I liked her, but I remember one particular night where we had a blast and she fell asleep on my couch. 💤 I put a blanket over her and went to bed in the other room. I woke up early and when I came out to see her, the makeup was gone and she was still sleeping, but she somehow looked even more beautiful than when I had left her! I thought to myself that I could wake up to that face for the rest of my life.” ❤️

Bridal Fashion: #PninaTornai 
Photos: @Stanlophotography 
Planning: @Dureevents
HMU: @Mua_ttt_tia @Unbleavablebridal
